<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>نادي الورديان الرياضي</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #0f172a 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            direction: rtl;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .background-animation {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1e3c8b20, #2563eb20, #059669/10);
            animation: gradientShift 10s ease infinite;
        }

        @keyframes gradientShift {
            0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 420px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            min-height: 100vh;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 0;
            animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(50px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c8b, #2563eb, #1e40af);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            animation: float 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            from { transform: translateX(-50px) translateY(-50px); }
            to { transform: translateX(50px) translateY(50px); }
        }

        .club-logo {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1e3c8b;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .club-logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05) rotate(5deg);
        }

        .club-info h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .club-info p {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.95;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .login-section, .dashboard {
            padding: 30px 25px;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            color: #1e3c8b;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1e3c8b, #2563eb);
            margin: 10px auto;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #1e3c8b;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .input-container {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-icon {
            position: absolute;
            right: 15px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 18px;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .form-group input, .form-group select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px 50px 15px 15px;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .form-group input:focus, .form-group select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #2563eb;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .contact-method-selector {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .method-card {
            padding: 20px 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .method-card.active {
            border-color: #2563eb;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        }

        .method-card i {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #1e3c8b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: block;
        }

        .method-card span {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .role-selector {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .role-card {
            padding: 20px 15px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .role-card.active {
            border-color: #2563eb;
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        }

        .role-card i {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #1e3c8b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .role-card div {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }

        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .btn:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c8b, #2563eb);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(30, 60, 139, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af, #3b82f6);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(30, 60, 139, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.8);
            color: #374151;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(209, 213, 219, 0.9);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn:disabled {
            background: #d1d5db;
            color: #9ca3af;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .verification-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05), rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.05));
            border: 2px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        }

        .verification-icon {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #0ea5e9;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        .otp-input {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .otp-digit {
            width: 55px;
            height: 55px;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        }

        .otp-digit:focus {
            border-color: #2563eb;
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
            background: white;
        }

        .timer {
            color: #059669;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .dashboard {
            padding-bottom: 120px;
        }

        .prayer-reminder {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #065f46, #059669, #047857);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(6, 95, 70, 0.3);
        }

        .prayer-time {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .profile-section {
            background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .profile-pic {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e5e7eb, #d1d5db);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 35px;
            color: #6b7280;
            border: 4px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .social-links a {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c8b, #2563eb);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(30, 60, 139, 0.4);
        }

        .nav-bottom {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.5);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 -5px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-item {
            text-align: center;
            color: #6b7280;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-width: 60px;
        }

        .nav-item.active {
            color: #1e3c8b;
            background: rgba(30, 60, 139, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .nav-item i {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .nav-item span {
            font-size: 12px;
            display: block;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .message {
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            animation: slideDown 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .success-message {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dcfce7, #bbf7d0);
            border: 2px solid #16a34a;
            color: #15803d;
        }

        .error-message {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2, #fecaca);
            border: 2px solid #ef4444;
            color: #dc2626;
        }

        .info-message {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
            border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
            color: #92400e;
        }

        .hidden {
            display: none;
        }

        .loading {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border-top-color: white;
            animation: spin 1s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .category {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .category:hover {
            transform: translateX(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .schedule-item {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #059669;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .schedule-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .schedule-time {
            color: #059669;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 100%;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .role-selector {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 12px;
            }
            
            .contact-method-selector {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 12px;
            }
        }

        .fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="background-animation"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="club-logo">
                <i class="fas fa-futbol" style="font-size: 40px; color: #1e3c8b;"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="club-info">
                <h1>نادي الورديان الرياضي</h1>
                <p>Al Wardian Sports Club</p>
                <p>تأسس عام 1926 - القاهرة، مصر</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Login Section -->
        <div id="loginSection" class="login-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">مرحباً بك</h2>
            
            <div class="role-selector">
                <div class="role-card" onclick="selectRole('coach')">
                    <i class="fas fa-whistle"></i>
                    <div>مدرب</div>
                </div>
                <div class="role-card" onclick="selectRole('player')">
                    <i class="fas fa-running"></i>
                    <div>لاعب</div>
                </div>
                <div class="role-card" onclick="selectRole('admin')">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
                    <div>إداري</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="contact-method-selector">
                <div class="method-card active" onclick="selectContactMethod('phone')">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    <span>رقم الهاتف</span>
                </div>
                <div class="method-card" onclick="selectContactMethod('email')">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    <span>البريد الإلكتروني</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <form id="loginForm" onsubmit="login(event)">
                <div id="phoneGroup" class="form-group">
                    <label>رقم الهاتف</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="tel" id="phone" placeholder="+20 101 234 5678" maxlength="15">
                    </div>
                    <small style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 8px; display: block;">
                        مثال: +20 101 234 5678
                    </small>
                </div>

                <div id="emailGroup" class="form-group hidden">
                    <label>البريد الإلكتروني</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="example@gmail.com">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>كلمة المرور</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="password" id="password" required placeholder="••••••••">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <span id="loginBtnText">تسجيل الدخول</span>
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="showRegister()">إنشاء حساب جديد</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Registration Section -->
        <div id="registerSection" class="login-section hidden">
            <h2 class="section-title">انضم إلى النادي</h2>
            
            <form id="registerForm" onsubmit="register(event)">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>الاسم الكامل</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-user input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="text" id="fullName" required placeholder="اكتب اسمك الكامل">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-method-selector">
                    <div class="method-card active" onclick="selectRegContactMethod('phone')">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                        <span>رقم الهاتف</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="method-card" onclick="selectRegContactMethod('email')">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        <span>البريد الإلكتروني</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="regPhoneGroup" class="form-group">
                    <label>رقم الهاتف</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="tel" id="regPhone" placeholder="+20 101 234 5678" maxlength="15">
                    </div>
                    <small style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 8px; display: block;">
                        مثال: +20 101 234 5678
                    </small>
                </div>

                <div id="regEmailGroup" class="form-group hidden">
                    <label>البريد الإلكتروني</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="email" id="regEmail" placeholder="example@gmail.com">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>كلمة المرور</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="password" id="regPassword" required minlength="6" placeholder="••••••••">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>تأكيد كلمة المرور</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock input-icon"></i>
                        <input type="password" id="confirmPassword" required minlength="6" placeholder="••••••••">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>نوع الحساب</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-users input-icon"></i>
                        <select id="userRole" required onchange="toggleAgeGroup()">
                            <option value="">اختر نوع الحساب</option>
                            <option value="player">لاعب</option>
                            <option value="coach">مدرب</option>
                            <option value="admin">إداري</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="playerAgeGroup" class="form-group hidden">
                    <label>الفئة العمرية</label>
                    <div class="input-container">
                        <i class="fas fa-birthday-cake input-icon"></i>
                        <select id="ageGroup">
                            <option value="">اختر الفئة العمرية</option>
                            <option value="youth">شباب (2006-2011)</option>
                            <option value="juniors">براعم (2012-2020)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <span id="registerBtnText">التالي - التحقق</span>
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="showLogin()">العودة لتسجيل الدخول</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <!-- Verification Section -->
        <div id="verificationSection" class="login-section hidden">
            <h2 class="section-title">التحقق من الهوية</h2>
            
            <div id="emailVerificationMsg" class="info-message hidden">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope-open-text"></i>
                تم إرسال رابط التحقق إلى بريدك الإلكتروني. يرجى فتح الرسالة والنقر على الرابط للمتابعة.
            </div>
            
            <div class="verification-container" id="phoneVerificationContainer">
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt verification-icon"></i>
                <p>تم إرسال رمز التحقق إلى:</p>
                <strong id="verificationContact"></strong>
                
                <div class="otp-input">
                    <input type="text" class="otp-digit" maxlength="1" id="otp1" oninput="moveToNext(this, 'otp2')">
                    <input type="text" class="otp-digit" maxlength="1" id="otp2" oninput="moveToNext(this, 'otp3')" onkeydown="moveToPrev(event, 'otp1')">
                    <input type="text" class="otp-digit" maxlength="1" id="otp3" oninput="moveToNext(this, 'otp4')" onkeydown="moveToPrev(event, 'otp2')">
                    <input type="text" class="otp-digit" maxlength="1" id="otp4" onkeydown="moveToPrev(event, 'otp3')">
                </div>
                
                <div class="timer" id="timer">إعادة الإرسال خلال: <span id="countdown">120</span> ثانية</div>
            </div>

            <button id="verifyBtn" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="verifyCode()">
                <span>تأكيد الرمز</span>
            </button>
            <button id="resendBtn" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="resendCode()" disabled>إعادة إرسال الرمز</button>
            <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="backToLogin()">العودة</button>
